# This git repo is rooted at the home folder, but it should only ever
# contain the MapFolio project. Ignore everything else by default so that
# `git add -A` / `git add .` from the home directory can never accidentally
# stage personal files (Documents, Pictures, AppData, etc).
/*

# Allow the path down to the MapFolio project folder
!/Visual Materials/
/Visual Materials/*
!/Visual Materials/My projects/
/Visual Materials/My projects/*
!/Visual Materials/My projects/AI/
/Visual Materials/My projects/AI/*
!/Visual Materials/My projects/AI/Gemenai project/
/Visual Materials/My projects/AI/Gemenai project/*
!/Visual Materials/My projects/AI/Gemenai project/better version cloude/
